Package com.norswap.nanoeth.trees.patricia

Class PatriciaTree

java.lang.Object
com.norswap.nanoeth.trees.patricia.PatriciaTree
@Wrapper
public class PatriciaTree
extends Object
Naive implementation of the Modified Merkle Patricia Tree, as per appendix D of the yellowpaper.

See trees.patricia package README for more information on patricia trees.

This uses the in-memory implementation (from the memory sub-package) by default. However the implementation can be changed by sub-classing. In particular, to use a more efficient implementation it is only necessary to implement the PatriciaNode interface, then subclass the present class, overriding the createLeafNode(Nibbles, byte[]) method to return an instance of the new node implementation.
